Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.03,0:01:47.78,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Where does the truth lie for us？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.78,0:01:54.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}象徴を失って迷い始める大衆よ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.62,0:01:59.17,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Trust in everything that you believe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.30,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Living in this chaotic new world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.30,0:02:05.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}今、目を澄ます
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.63,0:02:09.18,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Trust in yourself not what they believe
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.18,0:02:12.47,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}幻想の解の先へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.47,0:02:17.48,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}さあ騒然とノイズ　響く最中を
